Mention all contributors in the copyright file shipped by Debian.

Debian: change qrazercfg[-applet] arch to all

qrazercfg and qrazercfg-applet ship Python scripts, so they are
architecture-independent and thus can be marked arch "all" to avoid
rebuilding for every architecture.
